title: Two Guys 26th Anniversary Party!
itunes:title: Two Guys 26th Anniversary Party!
description: Recorded live from the Two Guys Smoke Shop 26th Anniversary party with a "who's-who" list of the industry's hottest Cigar-Lebrities!  Get as close to the action as possible on the night Dave gave away his classic 1936 Cadillac Fleetwood (Virgin in every way).  It's time for the finer things in life...It's time for the Cigar Authority.
